==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Retromingent
<hw>Re`tro*min"gent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>retro-</ets> + L. <ets>mingens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>mingere</ets>
to urinate.]</ety> <def>Organized so as to discharge the urine
backward.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>An animal
that discharges its urine backward.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Retropulsive</ent>⟦br⟧
